<dl><dt> <span class="script">template.XULMeth2("checkAdjacentElement", "( dir )")</span> </dt><dd> Return type: <em>no return value</em> </dd><dd> Deselects the currently selected <span class="script">template.XULElem("radio")</span> button in the group and selects the one adjacent to it. If the argument <var>dir</var> is <code>true</code>, the next radio button is selected. If it is <code>false</code>, the previous radio button is selected. </dd></dl>
